translations.skillmoveslikelihood_tooltip: Determines CPU frequency of using skills.
translations.internationalrep_tooltip:
Determines how well respected the player is in world football.
Different level will influence Career Mode decisions of player.
translations.is_unsackable_tooltip: The Board will never sack you, no matter how bad you are ;)
translations.perfect_timed_shot_tooltip: Your too early taped shoots (red & orange) will be automatically converted to perfectly timed shoots (green). If your second tap will be too late (grey) then this feature won't work.
translations.generate_ya_report_tooltip: Immediately generate new youth academy scout report. You need to have scouts sent on missions
translations.reveal_player_data_tooltip: Reveal player attributes in Global Transfer Network. You don't need to scout players with this
translations.modifier_tooltip:
Modifier - Modifies player overall rating without editing attributes.
i.e if player real ovr is 80 and modifier is 2 then in game player ovr will be 82.
translations.crossing_tooltip: A good Crossing attribute will increase the chances of finding your team mates & avoiding the opposition.
translations.finishing_tooltip: A good Finishing attribute will increase your chances of beating the keeper with shots inside the box.
translations.headingaccuracy_tooltip: A good Heading Accuracy will increase your timing & improve your accuracy when heading at goal.
translations.shortpassing_tooltip: The better your Short Passing, the less likely it will be that your player misplaces passes.
translations.volleys_tooltip: A good rating will increase your chances of connecting & scoring with a Volley to leave the keeper helpless.
translations.defensiveawareness_tooltip: Increasing your Marking attribute will improve the default position your player takes up when your team is not in possession of the ball.
translations.standingtackle_tooltip: A good Standing Tackle rating will mean you are more likely to come out with the ball when putting your foot in.
translations.slidingtackle_tooltip: The higher the value the greater your chance of being successful with Sliding Tackles.
translations.dribbling_tooltip: It enables a player to take faster touches on the ball, allows them to make faster dribbling turns, and gives them the ability to recover the ball from tackles better.
translations.curve_tooltip: The higher your Curve rating the more bend & swerve you'll get on the ball when shooting & crossing.
translations.freekickaccuracy_tooltip: A high Free Kick Accuracy increases your chances of avoiding the wall & beating the keeper from dead ball situations.
translations.longpassing_tooltip: Increase your Long Passing to turn defence into attack with improved accuracy & more powerful lobbed passes.
translations.ballcontrol_tooltip: The better your Ball Control, the more likely your player will be to take a good first touch when receiving the ball.
translations.shotpower_tooltip: The higher your Shot Power the more venom you'll get on shots of any type & from any distance.
translations.jumping_tooltip: The higher your jumping the more likely you'll be to beat opposition players to aerial balls.
translations.stamina_tooltip: A good Stamina rating will increase the amount of time your player can spend sprinting during a game as well as improve recovery time.
translations.strength_tooltip: Strength will increase your chances of winning physical challenges with opposition players.
translations.longshots_tooltip: The better your Long Shots the more likely you'll be to beat the keeper with shots from outside the box.
translations.acceleration_tooltip: Increasing your Acceleration will improve your player's speed off the mark & reduce the time it takes to reach your maximum Sprint Speed
translations.sprintspeed_tooltip: Modifies the maximum sprint speed a player can reach
translations.agility_tooltip: Agile players can turn quicker & are more likely to attempt spectacular headers, volleys & bicycle kicks.
translations.reactions_tooltip: Good reactions will allow you to latch onto loose balls & rebounds quicker than other players.
translations.balance_tooltip: A good Balance rating will reduce your chances of stumbling & falling when challenged by an opponent.
translations.aggression_tooltip: Aggression will increase your chances of coming out on top in a 50/50 challenge with the opposition.
translations.composure_tooltip:
Determines at what distance the player with ball starts feeling pressure from the opponent.
Affects the chances of making an error when shoot, pass and cross.
translations.interceptions_tooltip: Increases your ability to intercept passes made by your opponents
translations.positioning_tooltip: The higher the rating the better your player will position themselves by default following the ball going out of play.
translations.vision_tooltip: Vision will increase your ability to play accurate & intricate through balls to set up your team mates with scoring chances.
translations.penalties_tooltip: A good rating will increase your chances of tucking away Penalties & give the keeper no chance.
translations.gkdiving_tooltip: Help the goalkeeper play faster, more accurate dives. Also, helps be more successful when diving at an attacker in a 1 on 1 situation.
translations.gkhandling_tooltip: Increases the GKs ability to grab the ball with his hands. High attribute will cause the GK to be faster to grab the ball.
translations.gkkicking_tooltip: Goalkeeper Kicking defines how far a keeper can kick the ball during goal kicks and drop kicks.
translations.gkpositioning_tooltip:
Affects how well the GK is at placing himself correctly in his goal.
GK with good positioning will more likely be in the correct place in his goal to defend against all types of shots.
translations.gkreflexes_tooltip:
Affect the GKs ability to quickly react to shots or deflections.
Player with high Reflex attributes will be able to better react to deflections, and be faster to react to shots, free kicks, and penalty kicks.
They will also be faster when trying to dive at a players feet to strip the ball off them
translations.trait1_0_tooltip: Performs finesse shots faster with additional curve and improved accuracy.
translations.trait1_1_tooltip: Performs chip shots faster and with greater accuracy.
translations.trait1_2_tooltip: Performs power shots faster and with increased speed.
translations.trait1_3_tooltip: Set pieces are delivered with increased speed, curve, and accuracy. Ball trajectory preview line is longer.
translations.trait1_4_tooltip: Performs headers with increased power and accuracy.
translations.trait1_5_tooltip: Through Passes are more accurate, Swerve Passes are delivered with more curve, and Precision Passes travel faster to the destination.
translations.trait1_6_tooltip: Passes travel faster along the ground without impacting the trapping difficulty of the receiver.
translations.trait1_7_tooltip: Lob and Lofted Through Passes are more accurate, travel faster and are more difficult to intercept.
translations.trait1_8_tooltip: Executes difficult first-time Ground Passes with high accuracy, using backheels when contextually appropriate. Short distance Ground Passes are highly accurate.
translations.trait1_9_tooltip: All crosses are highly accurate, travel faster and with more curve.
translations.trait1_10_tooltip: Increased max speed of Sprint Jockey and improved transition speed from jockey to sprint.
translations.trait1_11_tooltip: Increased reach when performing blocks and improved ability to make a successful block.
translations.trait1_12_tooltip: Increased reach and improved chances of retaining possession of the ball when performing interceptions.
translations.trait1_13_tooltip: Improved chances of standing tackle success and grants the ability to stop the ball directly at their feet when performing a standing tackle.
translations.trait1_14_tooltip: Grants the ability to stop the ball directly at their feet when performing a slide tackle.
translations.trait1_15_tooltip: Greater strength when performing physical tackles.
translations.trait1_16_tooltip: Reaches a higher speed when performing Controlled Sprint and performs wide turns while dribbling with more precision.
translations.trait1_17_tooltip: Reaches a higher sprint speed while dribbling and has reduced chance of an error when sprinting or performing knock-ons.
translations.trait1_18_tooltip: Fancy passes and shots are performed with improved accuracy. Performs Flair animations when contextually appropriate.
translations.trait1_19_tooltip: Has reduced error when trapping the ball and is able to transition to dribbling faster with greater control.
translations.trait1_20_tooltip: Grants the ability to perform unique flick Skill Moves.
translations.trait1_21_tooltip: Keeps close control of the ball while dribbling at jog speed and can shield the ball more effectively from stronger opponents.
translations.trait1_23_tooltip: Reduces fatigue loss during play and increases fatigue recovery during half time.
translations.trait1_24_tooltip: Contextually triggers 'outside of the foot' passes and shots.
translations.trait1_25_tooltip: Performs volleys with improved accuracy and has access to acrobatic volley animations.
translations.trait1_26_tooltip: Performs throw-ins with increased power to cover a greater distance.
translations.trait1_27_tooltip: Performs higher jumps and has improved aerial physical presence.
translations.trait1_28_tooltip: Be a Goalkeeper players will have increased reach and handling closer to the end of the match.
translations.trait1_29_tooltip: Be a Goalkeeper players will have increased reactions and speed in 1-on-1 situations
translations.trait2_0_tooltip: Be a Goalkeeper players will have increased reflexes and reactions during opposing set pieces.
translations.trait2_1_tooltip: Be a Goalkeeper players will have increased speed when running.
translations.trait2_2_tooltip: Be a Goalkeeper players are more effective at saving shots from outside the box with increased reach and jumping.
translations.trait2_3_tooltip: Be a Goalkeeper players have increased reflexes and reactions when saving shots from inside the box.
translations.trait2_4_tooltip: Hidden Trait, CPU AI Only. Long Shot Taker
translations.trait2_5_tooltip: Hidden Trait, CPU AI Only. Early Crosser
translations.trait2_6_tooltip: Hidden Trait, Career Mode Only. Solid Player
translations.trait2_7_tooltip: Hidden Trait, Career Mode Only. Team Player
translations.trait2_8_tooltip: Hidden Trait, Career Mode Only. One Club Player
translations.trait2_9_tooltip: Hidden Trait, Career Mode Only. Injury Prone
translations.trait2_10_tooltip: Hidden Trait, Career Mode Only. Leadership
translations.icontrait1_0_tooltip: Performs finesse shots significantly faster with maximum curve and exceptional accuracy.
translations.icontrait1_1_tooltip: Performs chip shots more quickly with exceptional accuracy.
translations.icontrait1_2_tooltip: Performs power shots much faster and with a significant increase in speed.
translations.icontrait1_3_tooltip: Set pieces are delivered with exceptional speed, curve, and accuracy. Ball trajectory preview line is at maximum length.
translations.icontrait1_4_tooltip: Performs headers with maximum power and accuracy.
translations.icontrait1_5_tooltip: Through Passes are far more accurate, Swerve Passes are delivered with maximum curve, and Precision Passes travel at top speed to the destination.
translations.icontrait1_6_tooltip: Passes travel much faster along the ground without impacting the trapping difficulty of the receiver.
translations.icontrait1_7_tooltip: Lob and Lofted Through Passes are even more accurate, travel faster than ever, and are far more difficult to intercept.
translations.icontrait1_8_tooltip: Executes difficult first-time Ground Passes with even greater accuracy, using backheels when contextually appropriate. Short distance Ground Passes are exceptionally accurate.
translations.icontrait1_9_tooltip: All crosses are highly accurate, travel faster and with more curve. Performs driven crosses with exceptional power.
translations.icontrait1_10_tooltip: Increased max speed of Sprint Jockey and greatly improves transition speed from jockey to sprint.
translations.icontrait1_11_tooltip: Even greater reach when performing blocks and improved ability to make a successful block.
translations.icontrait1_12_tooltip: Even greater reach and improved chances of retaining possession of the ball when performing interceptions.
translations.icontrait1_13_tooltip: Significantly improved chances of standing tackle success and grants the ability to stop the ball directly at their feet when performing a standing tackle.
translations.icontrait1_14_tooltip: Greatly improved slide tackle coverage. Also grants the ability to stop the ball directly at their feet when performing a slide tackle.
translations.icontrait1_15_tooltip: Even greater strength when performing physical tackles.
translations.icontrait1_16_tooltip: Reaches even higher speed when performing Controlled Sprint and performs wide turns while dribbling with greater precision.
translations.icontrait1_17_tooltip: Reaches even higher sprint speed while dribbling and has greatly reduced chance of an error when sprinting or performing knock-ons.
translations.icontrait1_18_tooltip: Fancy passes and shots are performed with even greater accuracy. Performs Flair animations when contextually appropriate.
translations.icontrait1_19_tooltip: Has minimal error when trapping the ball and is able to transition to dribbling much faster with greater control.
translations.icontrait1_20_tooltip: Grants the ability to perform more unique ground and flick Skill Moves. Is significantly more agile when strafe dribbling.
translations.icontrait1_21_tooltip: Keeps exceptionally close control of the ball while dribbling at jog speed. Can shield the ball much more effectively from stronger opponents.
translations.icontrait1_22_tooltip: Accelerates significantly faster during Explosive Sprint.
translations.icontrait1_23_tooltip: Greatly reduces the long term fatigue effects on attributes, reaction time, and defensive awareness. Reduces fatigue loss during play and significantly increases fatigue recovery during half time.
translations.icontrait1_24_tooltip: Contextually triggers 'outside of the foot' of passes and shots. Reduced error on 'outside the foot' passes.
translations.icontrait1_25_tooltip: Performs volleys with significant accuracy and has access to unique acrobatic volley animations.
translations.icontrait1_26_tooltip: Performs throw-ins with more power to cover maximum distance.
translations.icontrait1_27_tooltip: Performs even higher jumps and has greatly improved aerial physical presence.
translations.icontrait1_28_tooltip: Be a Goalkeeper players will have greatly increased reach and handling closer to the end of the match.
translations.icontrait1_29_tooltip: Be a Goalkeeper players will have greatly increased reactions and speed in 1-on-1 situations
translations.icontrait2_0_tooltip: Be a Goalkeeper players will have significantly increased reflexes and reactions during opposing set pieces.
translations.icontrait2_1_tooltip: Be a Goalkeeper players will have greatly increased speed when running.
translations.icontrait2_2_tooltip: Be a Goalkeeper players are significantly more effective at saving shots from outside the box with greatly increased reach and jumping.
translations.icontrait2_3_tooltip: Be a Goalkeeper players have greatly increased reflexes and reactions when saving shots from inside the box.

translations.icontrait2_5_tooltip: Hidden Trait, CPU AI Only. Early Crosser
